</div></div></section></section><section id="floats-group1" class="floats-group"><section class="bt xbox font-sm" id="BX1"><h2 class="obj_head">HIGHLIGHTS.</h2>
<ul id="L1" class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li><p id="P65">This study presents an approach for helping select trial eligibility criteria.</p></li>
<li><p id="P66">It informs criteria’s impact on recruitment pool size and safety using EHR data.</p></li>
<li><p id="P67">It explores this approach through 3 case studies.</p></li>
<li><p id="P68">Case study findings demonstrate varying effects when choosing different criteria.</p></li>
</ul></section></section><section id="S19" class="ack"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Funding</h2>
